[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Chat Channels[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*]Create unlimited custom channels (staff, admin, VIP, etc.)
[*]Per-channel permission, prefix, format, and sound
[*]Toggle mode or one-off messaging
[*][ICODE]/ch join staff[/ICODE] or [ICODE]/ch staff Hello![/ICODE]
[/LIST]

[SIZE=4][B][COLOR=#00BFFF]Chat Filter Engine[/COLOR][/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][B]Cooldown[/B] – Rate-limit messages
[*][B]Spam detection[/B] – Jaro-Winkler similarity algorithm
[*][B]Censor mode[/B] – Replace bad words instead of blocking
[*][B]Banned words[/B] – Wildcard patterns from [ICODE].txt[/ICODE] files
[*][B]Anti-advertising[/B] – TLD blocking, phrase matching, regex
[*][B]Custom regex rules[/B] – Named rules with custom patterns
[*][B]Graduated punishments[/B] – Warn → mute → ban
[*][B]Command filtering[/B] – Filters apply to commands
[*][B]Violation logging[/B] – File + per-player records
[/LIST]

